PREREQUISITES:

An Image of a person with a Neutral facial Expression, front-faced. For best results, use portrait mode. Preferebly dimensions: height 1080px and width 600px

You can save and load expressions with the 'Load Exp Data' 'Save Exp Data' nodes.

\ComfyUI\output\exp_data\ <- Path to the folder being saved
